// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0007 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a42ab8ce-0f8d-5aaf-8757-ae823ff9544e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:4.0*")
